WEBVTT

00:01.537 --> 00:02.951
Can I borrow that book?

00:03.174 --> 00:04.640
It looks very interesting.

00:06.343 --> 00:07.207
Yes, you can.

00:07.465 --> 00:09.080
I just finished reading it.

00:11.053 --> 00:11.740
Thank you.

00:13.311 --> 00:14.870
Oh, I almost forgot.

00:15.077 --> 00:16.840
I also need to get a science book.

00:17.173 --> 00:18.409
May I borrow yours?

00:20.707 --> 00:21.283
Yes.

00:21.469 --> 00:22.167
Here you are.

00:23.672 --> 00:24.928
Thank you.

00:27.880 --> 00:29.725
Do you have a book that I can borrow?

00:31.663 --> 00:35.139
Yes, I have a new book by Stephen King that you might like.

00:36.671 --> 00:37.180
Thank you!

00:37.305 --> 00:38.662
I love Stephen King.

00:38.863 --> 00:40.535
I like all his stories.

00:43.228 --> 00:44.065
Here it is.

00:47.042 --> 00:48.993
May I also borrow this history book?

00:50.505 --> 00:51.139
Yes!

00:51.349 --> 00:52.021
Here you go.

00:52.204 --> 00:53.117
Happy reading!

00:55.184 --> 00:56.094
You, too!

